                "text": "<div class=\"rule\"><div class=\"rule-section\"><p class=\"rule-text\">Τα ρήματα που τελειώνουν σε <span class='special-text-1'>-ίζω</span> γράφονται με γιώτα.<br /><br />Εξαιρούνται τα ρήματα:<br />δακρ<span class='special-text-4'>ύζω</span><br />κατακλ<span class='special-text-4'>ύζω</span><br />αναβλ<span class='special-text-4'>ύζω</span><br />συγχ<span class='special-text-4'>ύζω</span><br /><br />δαν<span class='special-text-6'>είζω</span><br /><br />αθρ<span class='special-text-9'>οί</span><br /><br />πρ<span class='special-text-5'>ήζω</span></p></div></div>",
